This panel is used to view the index as a whole~~~or at least as much of
it as can be shown at a time. The index entries are always shown in the
correct order in accordance with the prevailing
[Sort As Rules xix_ref_sortas_rules.html].

To give the keyboard focus to this panel, press ~KAlt+I~E, or click it.
Once it has the focus, you can easily navigate up and down using
~KDown~E arrow, ~KUp~E arrow, ~KPage Down~E, ~KPage Up~E, ~KHome~E,
~KEnd~E, or by clicking the scrollbar. You can also navigate simply by
typing a letter to be taken to the first entry that begins with that
letter. You can even navigate if this panel doesn't have the focus, as
explained below.
(See also [Keyboard Shortcuts xix_ref_keys.html].)

